  <trk>
    <name>Tour de l&apos;éboulement des Diablerets</name>
    <desc>Hike around the landscape of Derborence, which was created by two colossal rockslides in the 18th century. A peaceful mountain lake, untouched forests, and a rich fauna – no wonder Derborence became a national nature reserve.</desc>
    <type>hikingTourTrail</type>
